<!channel>, Hannah we have matched you with Georgina as your E-Mentor. Feel free to introduce yourselves and continue chatting within this channel. Why not send a quick video to say hello! :wave:

I will now be leaving the channel, but please direct message myself or Emma if you have any questions. All the best! :smile:

Hi Hannah! So lovely to meet you. I’m at work at the moment so can’t chat for long but I’ll send you a little video when I get home tonight to get the ball rolling and then we can talk music! Have a great day!

Hello :grinning: :grinning: , it's nice to meet you too! I would send you a video too, but I don't like videos of myself (plus I have no means of taking one anyway haha). I look forward to your message later :slightly_smiling_face:. See you soon!

I think I'll just introduce myself in words. I'm better with words anyway haha. My name is Hannah (if that wasn't clear), I am 15 (mentally -6) and I'm just about surviving year 11 so far. My massive passion is Music. I play the piano and I kinda play guitar, and I love listening to music. I am a massive k-pop fan! "Massive" is an understatement; I'm more *O B S E S S E D* haha. I have a problem I know. I surprisingly enjoy playing classical pieces on piano more than I like playing songs. I'm working towards my Grade 6 in piano at the moment :grinning: . I also plan to study music in college. I've already applied for a BTEC Diploma in Music Technology and a BTEC Level 3 in Music Performance. I hope one day to study Music in uni as well, hopefully internationally too! I also love books and films (the book was better regardless the book- to - film adaptaion haha). I also really like food and bubble tea. I think that's about it?
